    <dashboard name='Story Sheet' type='storyboard'>
      <layout-options>
        <title>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#ff0000' fontname='Times New Roman'>Story Sheet</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </title>
      </layout-options>
      <style />
      <size maxheight='964' maxwidth='1016' minheight='964' minwidth='1016' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='2' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='98340' id='1' param='vert' removable='false' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98426' x='787' y='830'>
            <zone h='3527' id='3' type-v2='title' w='98426' x='787' y='830' />
            <zone h='10477' id='4' is-fixed='true' paired-zone-id='5' removable='false' type-v2='flipboard-nav' w='98426' x='787' y='4357' />
            <zone h='84336' id='5' paired-zone-id='4' removable='false' type-v2='flipboard' w='98426' x='787' y='14834'>
              <flipboard active-id='1' nav-type='caption' show-nav-arrows='true'>
                <story-points>
                  <story-point caption='Department-wise Patient Distribution and Resource utilizaton' captured-sheet='Patients By Department' id='1' />
                  <story-point caption='Gender-wise Patient Admission Analysis' captured-sheet='Patients By Gender' id='2' />
                  <story-point caption='Monthly Patient Admission Trend and Forecast' captured-sheet='Monthly Admissions Trend' id='3' />
                  <story-point caption='Department-wise Revenue Contribution' captured-sheet='Revenue By Department' id='4' />
                  <story-point caption='Most Frequently Diagnosed Diseases' captured-sheet='Top Disease' id='5' />
                </story-points>
              </flipboard>
            </zone>
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='27905' id='6' story-point-id='1' type-v2='text' w='80118' x='5217' y='49274'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman'>The department analysis highlights the patient load handled by each department. Departments with the highest admissions require additional doctors, nursing staff, and medical resources to maintain quality healthcare services and reduce waiting times. </run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='22303' hidden='true' id='7' story-point-id='2' type-v2='text' w='82480' x='5315' y='46784'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman'>The gender distribution provides insight into the proportion of male and female patients admitted to the hospital. This information helps management design targeted health awareness programs and allocate healthcare resources more effectively.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='22303' hidden='true' id='8' story-point-id='3' type-v2='text' w='63484' x='16142' y='53112'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman'>The monthly admissions trend helps identify seasonal patterns and changes in patient volume. By analyzing these trends and applying forecasting, the hospital can prepare additional staff, beds, and medical supplies for future demand.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='22303' hidden='true' id='9' story-point-id='4' type-v2='text' w='62598' x='32480' y='36411'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman'>Revenue analysis identifies the departments contributing the highest income to the hospital. These insights support better budgeting, investment planning, and resource allocation while highlighting departments that may require operational improvements.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='25104' hidden='true' id='10' story-point-id='5' type-v2='text' w='67913' x='12992' y='33817'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman'>Disease analysis reveals the most frequently diagnosed conditions among patients. Understanding disease patterns enables the hospital to improve preventive care, maintain adequate medicine inventory, and ensure specialist availability for high-demand conditions.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
      <simple-id uuid='{15BF9E67-E108-4C11-9F63-0C067014A696}' />
    </dashboard>
  </dashboards>
